  <p class="footnotetext"><a name="fn2" id="fn2">2</a> Rule 1.3 is entitled "Diligence" and provides, "A lawyer shall
  act with reasonable diligence and promptness in representing a client."</p>

  <p class="footnotetext"><a name="fn3" id="fn3">3</a> ODC characterized the Respondent's conduct as an "omission in
  that in each instance, he failed to file within the narrow deadlines required by applicable federal rules. In neither
